# Python Teaching Code

## Project description
This project is a website for a clothing brand. The goal is to create a clean online presence where customers can learn about the brand , view clothing items, and connect with future drops

## Features 
- Homepage for the brand
- About section
- Product or collection section
- Contact or social media links
- Simple navigation

## Tools used
- HTML
- CSS
- Javascript
- Github

## Future Improvements
- Add product images
- Add a Shopping Cart
- Improve mobile layout
- Connect social media pages
